---
import hero from "@images/hero.jpg";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---
<div class="overflow-hidden bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 sm:gap-y-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="lg:pr-8 lg:pt-4">
          <div class="lg:max-w-lg">
            <h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-lime-600">Conocenos primero</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-pretty text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl">Quienes Somos</p>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg/12 text-gray-600">Nuestra fundación nace del profundo deseo de crear un mundo más inclusivo y justo para todos, especialmente para los niños y niñas con discapacidad. Creemos que cada niño merece la oportunidad de desarrollar todo su potencial y vivir una vida plena.</p>
            <dl class="mt-10 max-w-xl space-y-8 text-base/7 text-gray-600 lg:max-w-none">
                <h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-lime-600">Nuestro trabajo</h2>
                <div class="relative pl-9">
                <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon" class="absolute left-1 top-1 size-5 text-lime-600">
                    <path fill="evenodd" d="M8.25 6.75a3.75 3.75 0 1 1 7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1-7.5 0ZM15.75 9.75a3 3 0 1 1 6 0 3 3 0 0 1-6 0ZM2.25 9.75a3 3 0 1 1 6 0 3 3 0 0 1-6 0ZM6.31 15.117A6.745 6.745 0 0 1 12 12a6.745 6.745 0 0 1 6.709 7.498.75.75 0 0 1-.372.568A12.696 12.696 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.305 0-4.47-.612-6.337-1.684a.75.75 0 0 1-.372-.568 6.787 6.787 0 0 1 1.019-4.38Z" clipRule="evenodd" />
                    <path d="M5.082 14.254a8.287 8.287 0 0 0-1.308 5.135 9.687 9.687 0 0 1-1.764-.44l-.115-.04a.563.563 0 0 1-.373-.487l-.01-.121a3.75 3.75 0 0 1 3.57-4.047ZM20.226 19.389a8.287 8.287 0 0 0-1.308-5.135 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 3.57 4.047l-.01.121a.563.563 0 0 1-.373.486l-.115.04c-.567.2-1.156.349-1.764.441Z" />
                  </svg>
                  
                  Asistencia integral para personas con discapacidad
                </dt>
                <dd class="inline">Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Maiores impedit perferendis suscipit eaque, iste dolor cupiditate blanditiis ratione.</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="relative pl-9">
                <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="absolute left-1 top-1 size-5 text-lime-600">
                        <path d="M9.375 3a1.875 1.875 0 0 0 0 3.75h1.875v4.5H3.375A1.875 1.875 0 0 1 1.5 9.375v-.75c0-1.036.84-1.875 1.875-1.875h3.193A3.375 3.375 0 0 1 12 2.753a3.375 3.375 0 0 1 5.432 3.997h3.943c1.035 0 1.875.84 1.875 1.875v.75c0 1.036-.84 1.875-1.875 1.875H12.75v-4.5h1.875a1.875 1.875 0 1 0-1.875-1.875V6.75h-1.5V4.875C11.25 3.839 10.41 3 9.375 3ZM11.25 12.75H3v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25h6v-9ZM12.75 12.75v9h6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-6.75h-9Z" />
                    </svg>
                      
                  Comidas nutritivas para infantes sin recursos.
                </dt>
                <dd class="inline">Anim aute id magna aliqua ad ad non deserunt sunt. Qui irure qui lorem cupidatat commodo.</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="relative pl-9">
                <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="absolute left-1 top-1 size-5 text-lime-600">
                        <path d="M11.47 3.841a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0l8.69 8.69a.75.75 0 1 0 1.06-1.061l-8.689-8.69a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-3.182 0l-8.69 8.69a.75.75 0 1 0 1.061 1.06l8.69-8.689Z" />
                        <path d="m12 5.432 8.159 8.159c.03.03.06.058.091.086v6.198c0 1.035-.84 1.875-1.875 1.875H15a.75.75 0 0 1-.75-.75v-4.5a.75.75 0 0 0-.75-.75h-3a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75V21a.75.75 0 0 1-.75.75H5.625a1.875 1.875 0 0 1-1.875-1.875v-6.198a2.29 2.29 0 0 0 .091-.086L12 5.432Z" />
                      </svg>
                      
                  Impactar con buenos actos una población desfavorecida
                </dt>
                <dd class="inline">Ac tincidunt sapien vehicula erat auctor pellentesque rhoncus. Et magna sit morbi lobortis.</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>
        </div>
        <Image
		src={hero}
		alt="Fundacion Hero"
		loading="eager"
		width={2432}
		height={1442}
		class="w-[48rem] max-w-none rounded-xl shadow-xl ring-1 ring-gray-400/10 sm:w-[57rem] md:-ml-4 lg:-ml-0"
	    />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>